AB The field of retailing has experienced significant changes in recent
   years. In this article, we review articles published in Journal of
   Retailing over the 2002-2007 time span, classified into ten broad topic
   categories: price, promotion, brand/product, service, loyalty, consumer
   behavior, channel, organizational, Internet, and other. Some areas have
   received a reasonable amount of attention; others would be worthy of
   additional work. We summarize a key insight from each article in the
